# ğŸŒ Setting Webhook on Linux Server

## Requirements
- Python 3.x
- Flask or FastAPI
- Public server (VPS or Replit)

## Example (Flask)
```python
from flask import Flask, request, jsonify
app = Flask(__name__)

@app.route('/api/payment-hook', methods=['POST'])
def payment_hook():
    data = request.json
    print("Received:", data)
    # Add your validation logic here
    return jsonify({"status": "ok"})

if __name__ == '__main__':
    app.run(host='0.0.0.0', port=5000)